questions.analysis:
由概率密度函数的性质知 $\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} f(x) d x=1$, 而
$$
\begin{aligned}
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} f(x) d x &= \int_{-\infty}^a 0 d x+\int_a^{+\infty} c \lambda e^{-\lambda x} d x \\
&= c \int_a^{+\infty} e^{-\lambda x} d(\lambda x) = -c e^{-\lambda x}\Big|_a ^{+\infty} = c e^{-\lambda a}
\end{aligned}
$$
所以 $c e^{-\lambda a}=1$, 从而 $c=e^{\lambda a}$. 于是
$$
\begin{aligned}
P\{a-1<X \leq a+1\} &= \int_{a-1}^{a+1} f(x) d x = \int_{a-1}^a 0 d x+\int_a^{a+1} \lambda e^{\lambda a} e^{-\lambda x} d x \\
&= -e^{\lambda a} e^{-\lambda x}\Big|_a ^{a+1} = -e^{\lambda a}\left(e^{-\lambda(a+1)}-e^{-\lambda a}\right) = 1-e^{-\lambda} .
\end{aligned}
$$
注意, $a-1<a$, 而当 $x<a$ 时, $f(x)=0$.
